title: I think riots trying to tell me something...

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body: I don't think I'm meant to play ranked...

replies.body:
pshhhhh thats nothing. Try going like a whole month with 3 wins in ranked. (last season I demoted from D5 - Plat 5 whoop whoop). So cut that even I had to make a big post - http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/gameplay-strategy/Ais2m0qd-my-ranked-journey-the-last-4-days-1-win-10-losses

It started with 1 win , 10 losses and just kept getting worse haha dark times for my ranked climb.
